WEBVTT

00:05:26.634 --> 00:05:31.696
then you will have spent
this day very well.

00:05:32.664 --> 00:05:34.664
(Music)

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:37.465
Begin by opening your eyes

00:05:37.489 --> 00:05:40.964
and be surprised
that you have eyes you can open,

00:05:42.217 --> 00:05:47.473
that incredible array of colors
that is constantly offered to us

00:05:47.497 --> 00:05:49.648
for our pure enjoyment.

00:05:51.942 --> 00:05:53.714
Look at the sky.

00:05:55.359 --> 00:05:57.732
We so rarely look at the sky.

00:05:58.834 --> 00:06:05.163
We so rarely note how different it is
from moment to moment,